WPPanorama
public static final class WPPanorama.FastScrollingBitmapDrawable
extends Drawable

Special WPPanorama.FastScrollingBitmapDrawable that draws a wallpaper as fast as possible.
Modified to include the ability to scroll the wallpaper infinitely.
Assumes no scaling.

Since:
2011
